    "status_headline": "Tank temperature holding steady at 92\u00b0F; main cooling hose stream deactivated; ~16,000 residents remain under evacuation orders in reduced zone (65% reduction from 50,000 peak); catastrophic explosion risk eliminated; MMA hardening in tank \u2014 Day 6.",
